---
globs: apps/b2c-frontend/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Role: Full-Stack Product Engineer.
Domain: Customer-facing iGaming platform.
Architecture: Multi-tenant application routed via subdomain proxy (Port 80). DO NOT use path-based routing.
Frontend: Components must be tenant-agnostic. Rely strictly on 'tenantId' for styling and logos. Use Tailwind CSS.
Backend: Use Next.js Server Actions for data mutation. All database queries (Prisma) MUST strictly filter by 'tenantId' to prevent data leakage between operators.
